## 11. Prohibited patterns

| Pattern | Why | Use instead |
|---------|-----|-------------|
| `<button>` raw HTML | Bypasses infra, inconsistent styling | Infra button component with variant SCSS class |
| `<select>` raw HTML | Never acceptable | `TS_DropDown` |
| `<label>` raw HTML | Layout inconsistencies, no error integration | `TS_PropRenderer.Horizontal` / `TS_PropRenderer.Vertical` |
| `<span>` for layout | Interacts poorly with flex/grid | Use layout primitives or semantic elements |
| `#id` as component root | Collides with `openContent` pop-up anchors, non-reusable | Use `.class` selector |
| Hardcoded hex colors | Breaks design system, un-themeable | `C.$primary-02`, `C.gray(5)`, etc. |
| Local `$font-color`, `$font-family` variables | Duplicates design system | Use `C.*` and `S.*` directly |
| `@import` in SCSS | Deprecated, causes duplication | `@use` with namespace |
| Wildcard `@use '...' as *` on external packages | Hides where names come from | Always alias external packages |
| `!important` | Sign of specificity conflict — fix the specificity | Restructure SCSS scope |
| `display: flex` / `flex-direction` on raw `<div>` | Bypasses layout primitives | `LL_H_C`, `LL_V_L`, etc. |
| `style={{ padding, gap, margin }}` | Design decisions belong in SCSS | SCSS class |
| `window.location` | Breaks routing history | `ModuleFE_Routing` |
| Direct entity mutation | Bypasses concurrency control | `EditableDBItemV3` |
| String arrays for tab/option lists | Untyped, no completion | String literal unions or typed constants |

